The paper deals with volume estimation of convex bodies, which is a topic in computational geometry (cs.CG). The paper also discusses the use of coordinate directions hit-and-run method, which is a technique used in optimization and linear programming (cs.DS). The reutilization of sample points is a technique used in machine learning and data analysis (cs.DM).
